{
  "page": "Queen Alysanne",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_(disambiguation)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alysanne (disambiguation)\">Alysanne (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<p><i><b>Queen Alysanne</b></i> is a war galley of the <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_fleet\" title=\"Royal fleet\">royal fleet</a> in service to <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>. It has one hundred oars.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The ship is presumably <a href=\"/index.php/Named_after\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Named after\">named after</a> Good Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Queen_Alysanne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Queen_Alysanne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Queen Alysanne</i> is part of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>'s fleet commanded by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Imry_Florent\" title=\"Imry Florent\">Imry Florent</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>. It is hit by burning pitch during the battle. It engages both <i><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_Silk\" title=\"Lady of Silk\">Lady of Silk</a></i> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/Lady%27s_Shame\" title=\"Lady&#39;s Shame\">Lady's Shame</a></i>. After <i>Lady's Shame</i> is sunk, <i>Queen Alysanne</i> is hit by <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a>, destroying her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Queen_Alysanne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_58\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 58\">Chapter 58</a>, Davos III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403104612\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.025 second